.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, green, red, white, yellow
5 different games are played: domino, canasta, mah-jongg, snooker, chess
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
There 5 different types of food: pineapple, peas, radish, tomato, lemon
City: miami, paris, hamburg, boston, new-york
1. the person playing domino is the person who likes red
2. the person playing swedish is the person traveling to hamburg
3. the person playing canasta is the person drinking tea
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white
5. the person who likes green is the person drinking coffee
6. the person eating radish is the person traveling to paris
7. the person who likes yellow is the person eating peas
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the person playing snooker is on the far left
10. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami
11. the person traveling to new-yorks is on the left or right of the person eating peas
12. the person eating pineapple is the person drinking beer
13. the person playing mah-jongg is the person eating tomato
14. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who likes blue
15. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| Game	|   snooker	|    canasta	|    domino	|    mah-jongg	|    swedish	|
| City		|     miami	|    new-york	|     paris	|     boston	|      hamburg	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Food		|   peas	|    lemon	|  radish	|    tomato	|   pineapple	|
